c: 5
v: 106
t: "Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe ! wa…óee seedee hakkunde mon, si maayde nden arii go…ó…óo e mon, tuma wasiyagol, [seedee…ìe] …ói…óo nun…óu…ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo'on, si tawii on yehii ka leydi masiibo maayde yanii e mon. Darnon …ìe ka batte julde, …ìe woondira Alla, si on sikkitike …ìe yo…ìetaake fii …óum coggu, hay si laatike joomiraawo badindiral, \"Men Suu…óataa seedee Alla on, menen ontuma [si men wa…óii …óum], haray men jeyaama e bakkondim…ìe …ìen"